<style>
  .about-container {
    max-width: 1200px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 40px 20px;
  }

  .about-header {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 60px;
  }

  .about-title {
    font-size: 48px;
    font-weight: 800;
    color: #1F2937;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    gap: 15px;
  }

  .about-subtitle {
    font-size: 20px;
    color: #6B7280;
    max-width: 700px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    line-height: 1.7;
  }

  .about-content {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
    gap: 30px;
    margin-bottom: 60px;
  }

  .about-card {
    background: white;
    padding: 35px;
    border-radius: 20px;
    box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);
    transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;
  }

  .about-card:hover {
    transform: translateY(-5px);
    box-shadow: 0 10px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
  }

  .about-card-icon {
    font-size: 48px;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
  }

  .about-card-title {
    font-size: 24px;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: #1F2937;
    margin-bottom: 15px;
  }

  .about-card-text {
    color: #6B7280;
    line-height: 1.7;
    font-size: 16px;
  }

  .mission-section {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #10B981 0%, #059669 100%);
    padding: 60px 40px;
    border-radius: 20px;
    margin-bottom: 60px;
    text-align: center;
    color: white;
  }

  .mission-title {
    font-size: 36px;
    font-weight: 800;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
  }

  .mission-text {
    font-size: 18px;
    line-height: 1.8;
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    opacity: 0.95;
  }

  .stats-section {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr));
    gap: 30px;
    margin-bottom: 60px;
  }

  .stat-card {
    background: white;
    padding: 30px;
    border-radius: 15px;
    text-align: center;
    box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);
  }

  .stat-number {
    font-size: 48px;
    font-weight: 800;
    color: #10B981;
    margin-bottom: 10px;
  }

  .stat-label {
    font-size: 16px;
    color: #6B7280;
    font-weight: 600;
  }

  .team-section {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 40px;
  }

  .section-title {
    font-size: 36px;
    font-weight: 800;
    color: #1F2937;
    margin-bottom: 40px;
  }

  .cta-section {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #D1FAE5 0%, #A7F3D0 100%);
    padding: 60px 40px;
    border-radius: 20px;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .cta-title {
    font-size: 32px;
    font-weight: 800;
    color: #1F2937;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
  }

  .cta-text {
    font-size: 18px;
    color: #6B7280;
    margin-bottom: 30px;
  }

  .cta-button {
    display: inline-block;
    padding: 15px 40px;
    background-color: #10B981;
    color: white;
    text-decoration: none;
    border-radius: 30px;
    font-weight: 600;
    font-size: 18px;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
    box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(16, 185, 129, 0.3);
  }

  .cta-button:hover {
    background-color: #059669;
    transform: translateY(-2px);
    box-shadow: 0 6px 12px rgba(16, 185, 129, 0.4);
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .about-title {
      font-size: 36px;
    }

    .about-content {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }

    .stats-section {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
  }
</style>

<div class="about-container">
  <div class="about-header">
    <h1 class="about-title">
      <span>🐾</span> About Pet Haven Hub
    </h1>
    <p class="about-subtitle">
      Connecting loving families with pets in need of homes. Our mission is to simplify and modernize the pet adoption process.
    </p>
  </div>

  <div class="mission-section">
    <h2 class="mission-title">Our Mission</h2>
    <p class="mission-text">
      Pet Haven Hub was created to bridge the gap between compassionate families and pets waiting for their forever homes. 
      We believe every pet deserves a loving family, and every family deserves to find their perfect companion. 
      Through our intelligent matching system and streamlined adoption process, we make it easier than ever to find your new best friend.
    </p>
  </div>

  <div class="stats-section">
    <div class="stat-card">
      <div class="stat-number"><%= Pet.where(available: false).count %></div>
      <div class="stat-label">Successful Adoptions</div>
    </div>
    <div class="stat-card">
      <div class="stat-number"><%= Pet.where(available: true).count %></div>
      <div class="stat-label">Pets Waiting for Homes</div>
    </div>
    <div class="stat-card">
      <div class="stat-number"><%= User.count %></div>
      <div class="stat-label">Happy Families</div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="about-content">
    <div class="about-card">
      <div class="about-card-icon">🏠</div>
      <h3 class="about-card-title">Find Your Perfect Match</h3>
      <p class="about-card-text">
        Our intelligent recommendation system helps you discover pets that match your lifestyle, preferences, and living situation. 
        We consider factors like pet size, energy level, and care requirements to ensure the best fit.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="about-card">
      <div class="about-card-icon">💝</div>
      <h3 class="about-card-title">Support Through Donations</h3>
      <p class="about-card-text">
        Can't adopt right now? You can still make a difference! Our donation program allows you to support pets in need, 
        helping cover medical care, food, and shelter expenses while they wait for their forever homes.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="about-card">
      <div class="about-card-icon">🎯</div>
      <h3 class="about-card-title">Streamlined Process</h3>
      <p class="about-card-text">
        We've simplified the adoption process to save you time. Browse available pets, submit adoption requests online, 
        and track your application status all in one place. No more endless paperwork or complicated procedures.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="about-card">
      <div class="about-card-icon"></div>
      <h3 class="about-card-title">Safe & Secure</h3>
      <p class="about-card-text">
        Your privacy and security matter to us. All adoption requests are handled with care, and our verification process 
        ensures that pets go to safe, loving homes. We're committed to protecting both pets and adopters.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="about-card">
      <div class="about-card-icon">👥</div>
      <h3 class="about-card-title">Community Driven</h3>
      <p class="about-card-text">
        Join a community of pet lovers dedicated to animal welfare. Share experiences, get advice, and be part of a 
        movement that's changing lives—one adoption at a time.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="team-section">
    <h2 class="section-title">How It Works</h2>
    <div class="about-content">
      <div class="about-card">
        <div class="about-card-icon">1️⃣</div>
        <h3 class="about-card-title">Create Your Profile</h3>
        <p class="about-card-text">
          Sign up and tell us about your preferences, living situation, and what you're looking for in a pet companion.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="about-card">
        <div class="about-card-icon">2️⃣</div>
        <h3 class="about-card-title">Browse & Discover</h3>
        <p class="about-card-text">
          Explore our database of available pets or let our recommendation engine suggest perfect matches based on your profile.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="about-card">
        <div class="about-card-icon">3️⃣</div>
        <h3 class="about-card-title">Submit Request</h3>
        <p class="about-card-text">
          Found your match? Submit an adoption or donation request with just a few clicks. Track your request status in real-time.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="about-card">
        <div class="about-card-icon">4️⃣</div>
        <h3 class="about-card-title">Welcome Home</h3>
        <p class="about-card-text">
          Once approved, it's time to welcome your new family member home! We'll guide you through the final steps.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="cta-section">
    <h2 class="cta-title">Ready to Make a Difference?</h2>
    <p class="cta-text">
      Whether you're looking to adopt or support through donations, every action counts. Start your journey today!
    </p>
    <%= link_to 'Browse Pets', pets_path, class: 'cta-button' %>
  </div>
</div>

<%= render 'shared/footer' %>
